1984;;The Rosebud Beach Hotel;;American;;Harry Hurwitz;;Colleen Camp, Peter Scolari, Christopher Lee;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Rosebud_Beach_Hotel;;After taking over a failing Miami hotel with her workaholic fiance, Elliot (Peter Scolari), Tracy (Colleen Camp) thinks model Monique Gabrielle is sleeping with him. She then tries to have an affair of her own, and arranges for hookers to become bellhops. Meanwhile, her father hires an arsonist to blow up the hotel.